Do follow the Steps To Get Customised Carousel - :)
	1- We need to install the dependency or library of slick slider carousel in our project.
		Step 1.1 - To install this slick carousel library.
			
			"npm install slick-carousel --save"
			"npm install ngx-slick-carousel --save"
		
		Step 1.2 - Specified import in your app.module.ts

			"import { SlickCarouselModule } from 'ngx-slick-carousel';"

		Step 1.3 - Do Specify the module in imports array
				"SlickCarouselModule",

		Step 1.4 - Open angular.json file and Specify the path in style array and js array
			"styles": [
              "src/styles.scss",
              "node_modules/slick-carousel/slick/slick.scss",
              "node_modules/slick-carousel/slick/slick-theme.scss"
            ],

			  "scripts": [
              "node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js",
              "node_modules/slick-carousel/slick/slick.min.js"
            ],	

		Step 1.6 - 	Copy the code as defined by file name
			
